202
00:19:54,865 --> 00:19:58,089
When the Buddha was asked, what is the taste of the Dharma?

203
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:02,094
He said, the taste of the Dharma was freedom.

204
00:20:05,057 --> 00:20:07,800
Well, I hope you found this talk interesting and helpful.

205
00:20:08,942 --> 00:20:10,824
May all of you be happy and peaceful.

206
00:20:11,505 --> 00:20:14,528
May all of you attain the nirvanic peace within.

